skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill

des: The American Medical Association is making it easier than ever to stay up-to-date on the latest health care news with the Morning Rounds flash briefing. Monday through Friday hear the newest stories on topics like physician burnout, public health issues, medical education and more.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
